Privacy Policy PLAYMOBIL Horse Farm
We welcome you to our PLAYMOBIL Horse Farm  App and thank you for your interest in our company, the geobra Brandstaetter Stiftung & Co. KG. In order to give you a good feeling with regard to how your personal data is handled, we would like to elucidate what happens to the produced data and which safety measures are taken by us.  Furthermore, you will be informed about your legally stipulated rights in connection with the processing of this data.
Contact
If required, contact us: +49 (0) 911/9666-0 or
service@playmobil.de
Right of information
On request we can notify you in writing whether and which personal data about you is stored.
Personal data & right of access
Via the PLAYMOBIL Horse Farm  App our company, the geobra Brandstaetter Stiftung & Co. KG, does not collect person-related data of the particular user. We merely acknowledge information about the type of your mobile device and the services that you call up or use thereby.
We cannot access other person-related data like telephone numbers or device codes resp. device identification numbers (e.g. IMEI Number).
The game course and the game options are stored solely on the mobile device, this is necessary to ensure the App functionality. These stored data are completely deleted as soon as the PLAYMOBIL Horse Farm  App is uninstalled.
Data transmission to third parties
Our company, the geobra Brandstaetter Stiftung & Co. KG, does not transmit any person-related data to third parties without your consent.
Ratings & reviews
Ratings (e.g. one to five stars) and reviews, which are released in our App, will be transmitted to our server. During the first data transmission, our server generates a random pseudonym for the transmitting App-entity. That affords the users to change their own ratings and reviews afterwards. The pseudonym is transmitted during all future ratings and reviews to our server but not during the call of contents.
We generate an aggregate evaluation out of the transmitted ratings of all users, to which all users of our App have access. We do not reveal the authorship of ratings or reviews, unless the authHorse Farmorship results from the content. Our App stores the ratings and reviews on the particular mobile device in order to show the users their own ratings and reviews.
We reserve the right to check and - if necessary - to lock or delete ratings and reviews afterwards, if there is any legitimate suspect of illegal use.
Date:
11.07.2017
Amendments
We reserve the right to adjust our Privacy Policy to the current legal position or when there are new features. The amended Privacy Policy is then valid for your next use of our App.
